sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Beheerder
    participant App as Kiosk App (Virtueel of Fysiek)
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant VB as Vision Box (Kiosk A)

    Note over Admin,App: Admin logt in via de app
    Admin->>App: Logt in en opent Admin Dashboard
    App->>API: GET /api/v1/kiosks [Met JWT Admin Token]
    API-->>App: 200 OK (Lijst van kiosken)

    alt 1. Locker Grid UI
        Admin->>App: Selecteert Kiosk A en opent Locker Grid
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/kiosks/{kiosk_id}/lockers
        API->>DB: Haal fysieke status van kluisjes op
        DB-->>API: Statussen (bijv. AVAILABLE, MAINTENANCE, OCCUPIED)
        API-->>App: 200 OK (Actuele status per locker)

        opt Forceer Deur Open
            Admin->>App: Tik op Kluisje 1 -> Forceer Open
            App->>API: POST /api/v1/lockers/1/open
            Note over API: Valideert Admin rol
            API->>VB: WSS: open_slot {locker_id: 1}
            VB-->>API: WSS: slot_opened
            API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_logs {action_type: 'ADMIN_FORCED_OPEN'}
            API-->>App: 200 OK (Kluisje geopend)
        end

        opt Markeer als Defect
            Admin->>App: Tik op Kluisje 1 -> Markeer MAINTENANCE
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/lockers/1/status {locker_status: 'MAINTENANCE'}
            API->>DB: UPDATE lockers SET locker_status = 'MAINTENANCE'
            API-->>App: 200 OK (Kluisje gemarkeerd)
        end

    else 2. Quarantaine Inbox
        Admin->>App: Opent Quarantaine Inbox
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/loans?status=PENDING_INSPECTION
        API-->>App: Lijst van loans in quarantaine
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/admin/evaluations/{evaluation_id}
        API-->>App: Foto, AI-rapport, damage details
        Note right of App: Zie [sequence_quarantine.mmd](./sequence_quarantine.mmd) voor afhandeling

    else 3. Asset Catalogus
        Admin->>App: Opent Asset Beheer
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/assets [Met JWT Admin Token]
        API->>DB: SELECT a.*, l.loan_status, u.first_name, u.last_name FROM assets a LEFT JOIN loans l ON a.asset_id = l.asset_id AND l.loan_status IN ('ACTIVE', 'RESERVED') LEFT JOIN users u ON l.user_id = u.user_id WHERE a.is_deleted = FALSE
        DB-->>API: Volledige lijst (Asset + Locker info + Lener)
        API-->>App: 200 OK (Beheerdersweergave)
        
        opt Nieuw Asset
            Admin->>App: Voegt asset toe
            App->>API: POST /api/v1/assets
            API->>DB: INSERT INTO assets
            API-->>App: 201 Created
        end
        
        opt Verwijder Asset (Soft Delete)
            Admin->>App: Verwijdert asset
            App->>API: DELETE /api/v1/assets/{asset_id}
            Note over API,DB: Soft-delete specifiek asset (catalogus/checkout filteren is_deleted = FALSE)
            API->>DB: UPDATE assets SET is_deleted = TRUE WHERE asset_id = {asset_id}
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end

    else 4. User & NFC Beheer
        Admin->>App: Opent User Beheer
        App->>API: GET /api/v1/users [Met JWT Admin Token]
        API-->>App: Lijst van gebruikers
        
        opt Deblokkeer User
            Admin->>App: Deblokkeert account
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/users/{user_id} {failed_login_attempts: 0, locked_until: null}
            Note over API,DB: Reset failed attempts & lock timer
            API->>DB: UPDATE users SET failed_login_attempts = 0, locked_until = NULL
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end
        
        opt Koppel NFC Tag
            Admin->>App: Koppelt nieuwe NFC tag
            App->>API: PATCH /api/v1/users/{user_id}/nfc {nfc_tag_id}
            Note over API,DB: Update kolom in users tabel
            API->>DB: UPDATE users SET nfc_tag_id = ?
            API-->>App: 200 OK
        end
    end